    "comment": "Rationale: Fig3 A-B: Both SNX16 and SNX16-GFP localized to several bright puncta in each synaptic bouton, which overlapped well with the early endosomal markers Rab5 and Rab4.\nFig3F: Immunoelectron microscopy with anti-GFP antibodies detected both SNX16-GFP and SNX16-GFP on early endosome and multivesicular like structures in the NMJ.\nFig S2: GFP and Snx16 in UAS-Snx16-GFP lines showed colocalisation indicating that the GFP antibody used for the localisation experiment are representative of snx16.. Experimental description: UAS-Snx16 and UAS-Snx16-GFP lines were constructed in pUAST (Brand and Perrimon, 1993) carrying the Snx16 cDNA (clone SD19533; Berkeley Drosophila Genome Project).",
